overview: It tells the story of three siblings namely Jep, Shuib and Mamat who lost their parents. Yet despite the absence of the parents, they are left with a secret will. They live life like ordinary village teenagers. It is difficult and easy to go through together until the time when the will can be read by them. Apparently, the three siblings will get a lot of property left by their parents but they must comply with the conditions set through the will. They have to go to town to find someone.
title: Lemang Aidilfitri Si Bujang Sepah
